  <main>
    <article>
      
      <h1>TikTok vs. Meta ROAS Bridge Calculator</h1>
      <p class="intro">Comparing TikTok ROAS to Meta ROAS directly is like comparing apples to oranges — their attribution windows are fundamentally different. This tool normalises both to a true blended picture.</p>

      <section class="card">
        <p class="card-title">Enter your details</p>
        <form id="calcForm" novalidate>
          <div class="field"><label for="metaAdSpend">Meta monthly ad spend (£/$/€)</label><input type="number" id="metaAdSpend" name="metaAdSpend" placeholder="e.g. 3000" min="0" required></div>
<div class="field"><label for="metaRevenue">Meta reported revenue</label><input type="number" id="metaRevenue" name="metaRevenue" placeholder="e.g. 9000" min="0" required></div>
<div class="field"><label for="metaWindow">Meta attribution window</label><select id="metaWindow" name="metaWindow" required><option value="">Select…</option><option value="1-day click">1-day click</option><option value="7-day click">7-day click</option><option value="7-day click + 1-day view">7-day click + 1-day view</option><option value="28-day click">28-day click</option></select></div>
<div class="field"><label for="tiktokAdSpend">TikTok monthly ad spend (£/$/€)</label><input type="number" id="tiktokAdSpend" name="tiktokAdSpend" placeholder="e.g. 1500" min="0" required></div>
