<details>
  <summary>Why are TikTok and Meta ROAS not directly comparable?</summary>
  <div class="faq-answer">Each platform uses different attribution windows and counting methods. Meta's 7-day click + 1-day view window will almost always show higher ROAS than TikTok's default because it credits more assists. Normalising to a consistent window reveals the true performance gap.</div>
</details>
